%% KServe Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-2.6/kserve.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as KServe Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as KServe Controller Manager<br/>controller-runtime v0.14.6
    participant KnSvc as Knative Service<br/>serving.knative.dev/v1
    participant VS as Istio VirtualService<br/>networking.istio.io
    participant Client as External Client
    participant IstioGW as Istio IngressGateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant KnGW as Knative Local Gateway<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant QueueProxy as Queue-Proxy / Activator<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant ModelPod as Model Server Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Storage as Cloud Storage (S3/GCS)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over User,Storage: Flow 1: Model Deployment (Serverless Mode)

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply InferenceService<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (kubeconfig)
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-...-inferenceservice<br/>HTTPS/TLS, API Server cert
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response (allow/deny)
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-pods<br/>HTTPS/TLS, API Server cert
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated Pod spec<br/>(inject storage-initializer, agent)
    K8sAPI-->>User: InferenceService created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch InferenceService<br/>HTTPS/TLS, ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: InferenceService event

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Knative Service<br/>HTTPS/TLS, ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Istio VirtualService<br/>HTTPS/TLS, ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ExternalName Service<br/>HTTPS/TLS, ServiceAccount Token

    Note over User,Storage: Flow 2: Storage Initialization

    Note right of ModelPod: Pod starts with init container
    ModelPod->>Storage: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, IAM credentials
    Storage-->>ModelPod: Model artifacts<br/>TLS 1.2+

    Note over User,Storage: Flow 3: Model Inference Request (Serverless Mode)

    Client->>IstioGW: POST /v1/models/{name}:predict<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS
    IstioGW->>KnGW: Forward via VirtualService<br/>HTTP/80, mTLS (Istio)
    KnGW->>QueueProxy: Route to activator/queue-proxy<br/>HTTP/80, mTLS (Istio)
    QueueProxy->>ModelPod: Forward inference request<br/>HTTP/8080, plaintext
    ModelPod-->>QueueProxy: Prediction response
    QueueProxy-->>KnGW: Response
    KnGW-->>IstioGW: Response
    IstioGW-->>Client: JSON prediction result

    Note over User,Storage: Flow 4: InferenceGraph Request

    Client->>IstioGW: POST to InferenceGraph<br/>HTTPS/443
    IstioGW->>QueueProxy: Route to Router pod<br/>mTLS
    QueueProxy->>ModelPod: Router fans out to node 1<br/>HTTP/80, mTLS (Istio)
    QueueProxy->>ModelPod: Router fans out to node N<br/>HTTP/80, mTLS (Istio)
    ModelPod-->>QueueProxy: Aggregated results
    QueueProxy-->>IstioGW: Combined response
    IstioGW-->>Client: Final response
